    "id": 8887,
    "title": "Bekendtgørelse om regulering af beløb i henhold til integrationsloven",
    "documentTypeId": "60",
    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "BEK nr 1035 af 16/12/1999",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Oversigt (indholdsfortegnelse)</div><DIV CLASS=PARA ID=\"OVERSIGT\"> \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<UL>  \r\n\r\n</UL>  \r\n\r\n</DIV><div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><DIV CLASS=PARA ID=\"INDHOLD\"> \r\n\r\n\r\n<FONT SIZE=5><P ALIGN=\"CENTER\">Bekendtg&oslash;relse om regulering af  \r\n\r\n bel&oslash;b i henhold til integrationsloven</P>  \r\n\r\n</FONT>  \r\n\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P>I medf&oslash;r af §&nbsp;48 i lov nr. 474 af 1. juli 1998 om integration  \r\n\r\n af udl&aelig;ndinge i Danmark (integrationslov) fasts&aelig;ttes:</P>  \r\n\r\n<DIV CLASS=PARAGRAF ID=\"P1\">  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=PARAB><B>§&nbsp;1. </B>Efter integrationslovens §&nbsp;48 reguleres  \r\n\r\n de i lovens §&nbsp;27, stk.&nbsp;1, § 29, §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;5 9, og  \r\n\r\n §&nbsp;59, stk.&nbsp;3 og 4, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b &eacute;n gang  \r\n\r\n &aring;rligt den 1. januar med satsreguleringsprocenten efter lov om en  \r\n\r\n satsreguleringsprocent.</P>  \r\n\r\n<I><P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Stk.&nbsp;2.&nbsp;</I>Satsreguleringsprocenten for 2000 udg&oslash;r  \r\n\r\n 3,2, jf. §&nbsp;1 i bekendtg&oslash;relse nr. 649 af 12. august 1999 om  \r\n\r\n satsreguleringsprocenten, tilpasningsprocenten og satstilpasningsprocenten  \r\n\r\n samt puljebel&oslash;bet for finans&aring;ret 2000.</P>  \r\n\r\n</DIV><!-- End of \"§ 1\" -->  \r\n\r\n<DIV CLASS=PARAGRAF ID=\"P2\">  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=PARAB><B>§&nbsp;2.</B> Med virkning for bel&oslash;b, der udbetales  \r\n\r\n i perioden 1. januar 2000   31. december 2000, g&aelig;lder  \r\n\r\n f&oslash;lgende:</P>  \r\n\r\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=4 WIDTH=264>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>1)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;27, stk.&nbsp;1, 1. led, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (introduktionsydelse for ikke-fors&oslash;rgere) <BR>  \r\n\r\n udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\"><BR>  \r\n\r\n<BR>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">5.294,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>2)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;27, stk.&nbsp;1, 2. led, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (introduktionsydelse for fors&oslash;rgere) udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">7.412,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>3)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;29, stk.&nbsp;1, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b (minimum  \r\n\r\n timesats) <BR>  \r\n\r\n udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">31,76 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>4)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;29, stk.&nbsp;2, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (besk&aelig;ftigelsestill&aelig;g) <BR>  \r\n\r\n udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">10,59 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>5)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;5, 1. pkt., n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (normalt grundtilskud) udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">3.600,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>6)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;5, 2. pkt., n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (nedsat grundtilskud) udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">2.011,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>7)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;6, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b (tilskud  \r\n\r\n vedr&oslash;rende aktivering) udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">5.506,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>8)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;7, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b (tilskud  \r\n\r\n vedr&oslash;rende kursus i samfundsforst&aring;else og danskundervisning)  \r\n\r\n udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">3.494,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>9)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;8, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b (tilskud  \r\n\r\n vedr&oslash;rende s&aelig;rskilt tilrettelagt danskundervisning) <BR>  \r\n\r\n udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">1.006,00 kr.</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>10)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;45, stk.&nbsp;9, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b (tilskud  \r\n\r\n efter udl&oslash;bet af introduktionsperioden) udg&oslash;r i:</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">&nbsp;</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>&Aring;r 1&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">3.070,00 kr.</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>&Aring;r 2&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">2.065,00 kr.</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>&Aring;r 3&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">1.006,00 kr.</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>11)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;59, stk.&nbsp;3, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (integrationstilskud til overgangsordning) udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">2.383,00 kr.</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR><TD WIDTH=\"62%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\"><DIR>  \r\n\r\n<P>12)&#9;Det i §&nbsp;59, stk.&nbsp;4, n&aelig;vnte bel&oslash;b  \r\n\r\n (aktiveringstilskud til overgangsordning) udg&oslash;r&#9;</DIR>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD WIDTH=\"38%\" VALIGN=\"TOP\">  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">&nbsp;</P>  \r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">1.482,00 kr.</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n</TABLE>  \r\n\r\n</DIV><!-- End of \"§ 2\" -->  \r\n\r\n<DIV CLASS=PARAGRAF ID=\"P3\">  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=PARAB><B>§&nbsp;3.</B>&nbsp;Bekendtg&oslash;relsen tr&aelig;der i  \r\n\r\n kraft den 1. januar 2000.</P>  \r\n\r\n<I><P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Stk. 2.</I> Samtidig bortfalder bekendtg&oslash;relse nr. 992 af 17.  \r\n\r\n december 1998 om regulering af bel&oslash;b i henhold til  \r\n\r\n integrationsloven.</P>  \r\n\r\n</DIV><!-- End of \"§ 3\" -->  \r\n\r\n<DIV CLASS=GIVET ID=\"GIVET\">  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=GIVET ALIGN=\"CENTER\"><I>Indenrigsministeriet, den 16. december  \r\n\r\n 1999</I></P>  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=SIGN1 ALIGN=\"CENTER\">Thorkild Simonsen</P>  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=SIGN2 ALIGN=\"RIGHT\">/Peter S. Willadsen</P>  \r\n\r\n</DIV><!-- End of \"GIVET\" -->  \r\n\r\n</DIV>",
